// ║  [+] Live Dollar P&L on active trade (price_diff × position_size ×        ║
// ║      contract_notional, routed through existing asset router)               ║
// ║  [+] PDH/PDL Context: Previous Day High/Low displayed in dashboard          ║
// ║      with status: Above PDH / Below PDL / Inside Daily Range                ║
// ║  [+] Tree-Format AI Narrative: ├── / │ / └── structured multi-TF view      ║
// ║      replaces flat R=/V=/F= rows — all 5 layers with RSI + score icon       ║
// ║  [+] Tree narrative also injected into War Room Telegram broadcast          ║
// ║  BASE: SA-GAIP v6.1 (all risk router bug fixes intact)                     ║
// ╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
// ║  BUG FIX (inherited from v6.1) — RISK MODEL ASSET ROUTER                  ║
// ║  FIXED: _risk_at_min_lot() was using forex math universally →              ║
// ║  10,000x leverage on crypto/ETH/BTC. All sizing routes through             ║
